der \u00e5 v\u00e6re hyggelig tilbake.", "Jeg har selv opplevd d\u00e5rlig kundebehandling, s\u00e5 jeg p\u00e5st\u00e5r ikke at alle butikkansatte er like serviceinnstilte. Men de aller fleste av oss vil gj\u00f8re v\u00e5r aller beste for at du skal v\u00e6re forn\u00f8yd n\u00e5r du forlater butikken. Det er tross alt det vi lever av."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "meninger"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "meninger|ordetfritt"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "896159324a4f38a347b0a9bf27c1612339ca5a99c682ca34f9754e9a4f492716"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-05-01T04:56:08.000Z"}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article13190004.ece/i2ei7t/ALTERNATES/w980-default/ta783609%20(2).jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/64b5488d94b1e9c5cbd1994ad8a6a2dfd797f4d1.jpg?598d7ca3"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "- Kj\u00e6re kunde, jeg blir daglig kjeftet p\u00e5 og utskjelt -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "64b5488d94b1e9c5cbd1994ad8a6a2dfd797f4d1"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["butikk", "Kundebehandling", "h\u00f8flighet", "priser", "frekk", "ansatte"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "butikk,Kundebehandling,h\u00f8flighet,priser,frekk,ansatte"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["ordetfritt", "meninger"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "personal-finance"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["pris", "butikk", "daglig kjeftet", "kunde"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": "kundebehandling"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["meninger", "meninger/ordetfritt"]}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article13190004.ece/i2ei7t/ALTERNATES/w980-default/ta783609%20(2).jpg"}, {"field": "og-locale", "value": "nb_NO"}, {"field": "og-site-name", "va